            "creation_date": 1429471529,
            "body": "<p>You can use generics.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public interface dataModel {\n   //nothing\n}\npublic interface dataRepo&lt;T extends dataModel&gt; {\n    public doIt(T a);\n}\npublic class concreteDataModel implements dataModel {\n    public doIt(dataModel a);\n}\npublic class concreteDataRepo implements dataRepo&lt;concreteDataModel&gt; {\n    public doIt(concreteDataModel a);\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 29734746,
            "question_id": 29734696
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://i.sstatic.net/1pefW.png?s=256",
                "account_id": 2529002,
                "user_type": "registered",
                "user_id": 2197700,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/2197700/anubian-noob",
